    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Cynotilapia chilundu. A. Holotype, PSU 12774, adult male, 82.9 mm SL, Taiwanee Reef, Lake Malaŵi, Malaŵi, Africa; B. Male in breeding coloration (approx. 75 mm SL) at type locality; C. Female (approx. 60 mm SL) at type locality." ;
